[src:prisma-client/global-objects-object] The constructor function that created the instance object.
[src:prisma-client/global-objects-object] For plain `Object` instances, the initial value is the `Object` constructor.
[src:prisma-client/global-objects-object] Instances of other constructors each inherit the `constructor` property from their respective `Constructor.prototype` object.
